297
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:04,319
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bilo ništa za Flutter i React Native.

298
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:07,599
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, jednostavno smo se odlučili za sto posto Native.

299
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,680
[SPEAKER_01] A za web smo koristili React.

300
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] Lijepo.

301
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:10,880
[UNKNOWN] Da.

302
